                    </div>
                    <span>Yes, ORDB does recommend this book for server administrators with open relay.  However, this server administrator found no information in the book that would be helpful in closing an open relay.  Complete waste of money and time.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">details the broad issues - not specifics</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
